  "prompt": "Can we load money in multi wallet ICICI card?",
  "response": "As of my last update, the ICICI Bank Multi Wallet card allows users to load money into the card for various purposes, such as payments and transactions. However, the ability to load money may depend on the features specific to your card and the services provided by ICICI Bank at the time.\n\nTo load money onto your ICICI Multi Wallet card, you typically have several options, including:\n\n1. **Online Transfer**: You might be able to transfer funds from your ICICI Bank account via online banking or the ICICI mobile app.\n\n2. **Cash Deposit**: You can deposit cash at an ICICI Bank branch or ATM that supports cash deposits.\n\n3. **Third-party Apps**: Some digital wallets or payment apps may allow you to load money onto your ICICI card.\n\n4. **USSD Codes**: If applicable, you may use USSD codes provided by the bank for loading funds.\n\nFor the latest information and specific instructions, it\u2019s best to visit the ICICI Bank website or contact their customer service directly. They can provide guidance on how to use and load money onto your Multi Wallet card effectively.",
